  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. Regulatory requirement ISO 13485 §7.3.6 and 21 CFR 820.30(g) are discussed in the narrative and an inline Requirement object is included in the package; the model must satisfy acceptance bounds of <10% QoI difference and E/uval < 1.96 per the pre-specified protocol.",
